{"tid":2101015,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【突發】保安局指向獲豁免強制檢疫者發逾20萬張醫學監察書","createTime":"2020-07-09T12:50:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-09T12:58:22.000Z","uid":259088,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"03b85bac12dd52dd668870c07ab3ac3dcbf7d6a7","tid":2101015,"uid":259088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T12:50:30.000Z","msg":"保安局表示，今年2月至5月在各出入境管制站，<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">向獲豁免進行14天強制檢疫人士，發出超過20萬張醫學監察通知書</span></span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n議會陣線立法會議員毛孟靜關注，自抵港人士必須接受強制檢疫14天的規例實施以來，每月有多少來自內地、澳門及台灣的人士，獲豁免遵守有關規定。<br />\n<br />\n保安局書面答覆指出，<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">今年2月共發出93602張醫學監察通知書、3月發出39211張、4月發出36039張，5月發出40220張。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n保安局表示，根據規例，<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">獲豁免進行14天強制檢疫人士，在留港期間要進行14天醫學監察，須戴口罩和每天量度體溫兩次，如有不適應向衞生署呈報。</span></span></strong>有關人士在入境時，均須通過衞生署在口岸進行的體溫監測和健康申報程序。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1536645-20200708.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1536645-20200708.htm&d=gCjj53haX7oQ0UVj6qLsjnRNzM9MViFDfs2457H6WAQ%3D&h=db2ec383\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1536645-20200708.htm&h=b01389d2\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1536645-20200708.htm</a>"},{"pid":"c47f3bc462005b64f9fabe08d1c0411412119ba8","tid":2101015,"uid":35296,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T12:51:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f6f79d8c97f5769e31e0d81444a4179a8bea7f1","tid":2101015,"uid":26333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T12:52:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2489de119212f7bbc3128d804991f36c35469347","tid":2101015,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T12:54:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5e55bf9dd29c4b92addba00977ee549b2fbaf7b","tid":2101015,"uid":259088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T12:58:22.000Z","msg":"香港係咪發緊夢 發出咗20萬張獲豁免都唔知<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}